{"id":469602,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Martin","text":"=\"preserve\">Helen Dorothy Martin (July 23, 1909 \u2013 March 25, 2000) was an American actress of stage and television. She was best known for her role as Weeping Wanda on the sitcom \"Good Times\" and as Pearl Shay on the sitcom \"227\". Martin was born in St. Louis, Missouri.\nMartin died of a heart attack on March 25, 2000 in Monterey, California, aged 90.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":73},{"uri":"Actress","surface_form":"actress","offset":82},{"uri":"Broadway_theatre","surface_form":"stage","offset":93},{"uri":"Television","surface_form":"television","offset":103},{"uri":"Sitcom","surface_form":"sitcom","offset":171},{"uri":"Good_Times","surface_form":"Good Times","offset":179},{"uri":"Sitcom","surface_form":"sitcom","offset":216},{"uri":"227_(TV_series)","surface_form":"227","offset":224},{"uri":"St._Louis","surface_form":"St. Louis","offset":249},{"uri":"Missouri","surface_form":"Missouri","offset":260},{"uri":"Myocardial_infarction","surface_form":"heart attack","offset":287},{"uri":"Monterey%2C_California","surface_form":"Monterey","offset":321},{"uri":"California","surface_form":"California","offset":331}]}